name: Oscar
description: Esiu Yeo is a Senior UI/UX Designer with over 10 years of experience. He has a strong foundation in digital marketing and a passion for creating user-centric solutions. His expertise includes user research, wireframing, prototyping, and UI design. He has worked as a Web Design Specialist at Maxis eCommerce since October 2021, where he sets design direction, prioritizes user needs, and collaborates with project managers and developers. Prior to that, he worked as a Web Solution Associate at Maxis eCommerce, Senior UI/UX Designer at Optima Innovation Sdn Bhd, and Visual Communicator at Creative Tomato Design & Digital Kitchen. He holds a Bachelor of Arts in Commercial and Advertising Art from Northumbria University and a Diploma in Commercial and Advertising Art from Limkokwing University of Creative Technology.
